    end

    %% ─── ECS FARGATE CLUSTER ─────────────────────────────────────────
    subgraph ECS ["  ☁️  ECS Fargate Cluster — docker-auditor  "]
        subgraph FE_SVC ["  📦  Frontend Service · 1–2 Tasks  "]
