            Internal · Port 8000
            Private VPC Only
            No Public Exposure"]:::aws

            BE["🐍 FastAPI 0.111.0 · Python 3.12-slim
            Uvicorn 0.29.0 · 4 Async Workers
            Pydantic v2 2.7.1 · Input Validation
