        ─────────────────────────────
        ci-cd.yml Stages:
          1. test-frontend  Node 20 · ESLint · Jest
          2. test-backend   Python 3.12 · pytest · Redis
          3. test-worker    Python 3.12 · pytest · Redis
          4. build-and-push docker buildx · layer cache
          5. deploy         ecs update-service
             Wait: 60 × 15s rollout timeout
        ─────────────────────────────
        terraform.yml:
          plan (PR) → apply (main) → destroy (manual)
          PR Comment: plan output ≤ 65 KB"]:::cicd

        TF["🏗️ Terraform — 14 Modules
        vpc  · ecs  · alb  · ecr
        cognito    · dynamodb  · s3
